    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2008 BMW M3, a purist's delight featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to deliver linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides crisp, rev-matched downshifts, while the GKN-sourced variable M differential lock ensures maximum traction out of the apex. This chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains tight, with no subframe issues or significant bushing play. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system refresh and a clean oil analysis, confirming the health of the rod bearings and VANOS solenoids. A driver-focused example that offers peak analog feedback with modern dual-clutch efficiency.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
